Team11 GOW: Oconee Co. vs. Morgan Co. WXIA 6:58 p.m. EDT October 16, 2015 #Team11 Game of the Week (Photo: 11Alive) CONNECT TWEET LINKEDIN COMMENT EMAIL MORE 
It came down to the wire in the voting, will the same be true on the field when Oconee County takes over Morgan County in the #Team11 Game of the Week brought to you by Academy Sports + Outdoors. 
It's a rivalry game. Morgan County will try to avenge Oconee's comeback victory in 2014. 
Oconee County enters the game 5-1, while Morgan County sits at 3-3. If Oconee County wins, they clinch a playoff spot. For Morgan County, a win would put them another step forward in their quest for a playoff berth. 
Watch full coverage tonight at 10:30 p.m. on TheATL and 11 on 11Alive. 11Alive's David Wilkinson previews the big game WXIA Team11 GOW: Oconee Co. vs. Morgan Co. (Part 2) WXIA
